WEBVTT

00:02:58.772 --> 00:03:03.354
Often we think about being able to do
diagnosis under a tree, off-grid.

00:03:03.816 --> 00:03:06.545
I'll tell you two examples
today of new tools.

00:03:06.569 --> 00:03:08.374
One of them starts in Uganda.

00:03:08.751 --> 00:03:10.280
In 2013,

00:03:10.304 --> 00:03:14.350
on a field trip to detect
schistosomiasis with Foldscopes,

00:03:14.374 --> 00:03:16.932
I made a minor observation.

00:03:16.956 --> 00:03:18.533
In a clinic,

00:03:18.557 --> 00:03:19.896
in a far, remote area,

00:03:19.920 --> 00:03:23.508
I saw a centrifuge
being used as a doorstop.

00:03:24.192 --> 00:03:26.583
I mean -- quite literally, the doorstop.

00:03:26.607 --> 00:03:28.333
And I asked them and they said,

00:03:28.357 --> 00:03:30.384
"Oh, we don't actually have electricity,